      .home__extras__about-us
        p.home__extras__about-us__text
          span.home__extras__about-us__text_span WHO WE ARE
          | An independent brand of <br>
          | urban trekking shoes and accessories <br>
          | that comes from a convergence of <br>
          | arts and personalities. <br>
      .home__extras__preview
        each product in products
          figure.home__extras__preview__item
            img.home__extras__preview__item__image(src='#')
      .home__extras__shop__button
        a.home__extras__shop__button__link(href='/') SHOP ALL

      .home__footer
